<page section="download">
  <heading>Download</heading>

  <content>
    <p>
      Go to <github-releases-stable /> and download <strong><workbench-download-file release="stable" wm="cocoa" os="macosx" arch="x86" /></strong>.
    </p>

    <div id="download-info">
      <img src="img/workbench-macos.png" class="pic" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;" alt="Carrot2 Clustering Workbench for Mac OS X Download" />

      <strong>After download completes:</strong>

      <ol>
        <li>
          Extract the archive and run <tt>carrot2-workbench</tt>
        </li>

        <li>
          Take a look at some <manual-link target="_blank" section="section.getting-started">common getting started scenarios</manual-link>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <p class="note">
        <strong>Note: </strong><c2 /> <dcw /> requires Mac OS 10.4 or later and Java for 
        Mac OS X Release 5 or later.
      </p>
    </div>
  </content>
</page>
